<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
     xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
     xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
     metal:use-macro="api.anonymous_layout">

  <div metal:fill-slot="content">

    <p>Unable to reset your password.  Try these troubleshooting tips:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>
            Verify you pasted the complete password reset URL from the email.
        </li>
        <li>
            If several days have passed since you initiated the request
            to reset your password, you should
            <a href="${api.app_url}/reset_request.html">try again</a>.
        </li>
        <li>
            Verify you entered the correct user name.
        </li>
        <li>
            Email your <a
            href="mailto:${api.settings.admin_email}">Site Administrator</a>
            for additional help.
        </li>
    </ul>
    <p><a href="${api.app_url}/login.html">Return to the login page</a></p>

  </div>
</html>
